    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great and drives even better? This car has been well-loved and is in wonderful shape for its next owner. It\u2019s super clean, handles like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it! I've taken really good care of it, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this beauty go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
