    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system for a broad power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. This example retains its mechanical purity with a balanced 50/50 weight distribution and a meticulously serviced high-pressure oil system, offering the quintessential analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
